    m_AlignByGeometry: 0
    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 1
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: You have always dreamed of swimming at the olympics and now you have your
    chance! The coach of the USA swim team has looked into your progress through
    the years and has given you a challenge. If you can win a race against his swimmers
    then you can join the team and go with them to the olympics! You have one shot
    to impress the coach, What will you swim?
